OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,FA Black-led Baptist church vandalised
OL,7,Fwith red crosses spray painted across
OL,8,Fthe building says it has reported the
OL,9,F"unacceptable" to police.
OL,11,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,12,Fafter two incidents of criminal damage
OL,13,Fwere reported at Newton Heath Chapel,
OL,14,FCulcheth Lane, Manchester.
OL,16,FMembers of the congregation found the
OL,17,FSt George's cross graffitied on the
OL,18,Fwalls and windows of the church, and
OL,19,Fbelieve it was targeted as a potential
OL,20,Fhate crime due to most of the
OL,21,Fworshippers that attend being black.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
