OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,FThe incident took place in the early
OL,7,Fhours of Saturday 6 September.
OL,9,FGreater Manchester police have said it
OL,10,Fis not being treated as a hate crime
OL,11,Fbut as criminal damage.
OL,13,FDr Olugbenga Olumodimu, the resident
OL,14,Fpastor said that the church were not
OL,15,Fgoing to "dignify the attack" and said
OL,16,Fhe didn't have "any business removing
OL,17,Fit."
OL,19,FThe pastor said: "We are a community
OL,20,Fwho sits together, we speak together,
OL,21,Fwe sing together, we eat together.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
