OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,F"Even this individual who has acted
OL,7,Fthis way will soon be overcome by the
OL,8,Flove of God, and perhaps soon be part
OL,9,Fof us.J"We just continue in the grace
OL,10,Fof God."
OL,12,FHe also said: "I was quite disgusted
OL,13,Fwhen I first saw crosses. But when I
OL,14,Fsaw the video and saw that it was one
OL,15,Fperson, there was no need to be too
OL,16,Fworried about it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
