OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,F"This sort of behaviour from one
OL,7,Fperson can be difficult to control.
OL,8,FNow that this has happened, I've asked
OL,9,Fthe team to put in some security
OL,10,Fmeasures to let us know that it's
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,F"Even if it's a lone ranger, I don't
OL,14,Fthink it's acceptable. I think it's
OL,15,Fvery unacceptable.
OL,17,F"It would be great if the police could
OL,18,Fidentify who this is and they can have
OL,19,Fa sit down and just talk to this
OL,20,Fperson and find out why you would be
OL,21,Fthis barbaric?"
