OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,FThe building was bought by the New
OL,7,FCovenant Church in 2024, and serves as
OL,8,Fthe Manchester North campus for the
OL,9,Freligious organisation.
OL,11,FLocal councillor, John Flanagan also
OL,12,Fsaid: "The church has been there for
OL,13,Fover 80 years and these plastic
OL,14,Fpatriots have painted the red St
OL,15,FGeorge crosses on it.
OL,17,F"The Baptist church is a predominantly
OL,18,Fa black community and they see it as a
OL,19,Fracist thing. They've gone too far.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
