OL,3,CBlack-led baptist church will not
OL,4,C'dignify' St George's cross vandal
OL,6,F"I support people wanting to put their
OL,7,Fflags up. If people want to put flags
OL,8,Fup on lampposts and stuff, that's up
OL,9,Fto them.
OL,11,F"But the desecration of a church is
OL,12,Foutrageous. Enough is enough.
OL,14,F"On behalf of the people of Newton
OL,15,FHeath, we are horrified."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
